## Verification Plan

### Automated Verification
- Run `seed_all_modules.ts`.
- Verify document counts per program in the DB.

### Manual Verification
- Verify the new "Programs" section exists in the library sidebar.
- Select a specific program (e.g., DCCM) and verify only relevant modules are shown.
- Check "Common Foundation" modules.
- Check the "Cheat Notes" formatting in the modal.
